com.android.volley.toolbox

Class JsonRequest<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.volley.Request<T>
      • com.android.volley.toolbox.JsonRequest<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - JSON type of response expected
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Request<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonArrayRequest, JsonObjectRequest

    public abstract class JsonRequest<T>
extends Request<T>
    A request for retrieving a T type response body at a given URL that also optionally sends along a JSON body in the request specified.

      • getBody

        public byte[] getBody()
        Description copied from class: Request
        Returns the raw POST or PUT body to be sent.

        By default, the body consists of the request parameters in application/x-www-form-urlencoded format. When overriding this method, consider overriding Request.getBodyContentType() as well to match the new body format.
